## Tools Used

| Tool | Version |
|------|---------|
| Xilinx Vivado | 2021.1 |
| VHDL Standard | VHDL-93/2008 |
| Target Device | Artix-7 (xc7a35t) |
| License | WebPACK (Free) |

---

## How to Run

1. Clone this repository
2. Open **Xilinx Vivado** → Create New Project
3. Add `vhdl/decoder_2to4.vhd` as design source
4. Add `vhdl/tb_decoder_2to4.vhd` as simulation source
5. Right-click `decoder_2to4.vhd` → **Set as Top**
6. Run **RTL Analysis** to view the schematic
7. Run **Behavioral Simulation** to verify the truth table

---

